My vote goes to Vladimir. As an melee, he is really annoying. If you have a ranged skill to poke, it still doesn't help, since he heals any poke you throw at him. If you manage to close the gap to him, he will pool away. Bonus points if he is running Phase Rush to be even safer at pooling away with bonus speed.
